org.drip.param.market

Class ComponentMarketParamSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.drip.service.stream.Serializer
      • org.drip.param.definition.ComponentMarketParams
        • org.drip.param.market.ComponentMarketParamSet

  • public class ComponentMarketParamSet
extends ComponentMarketParams
    This class provides implementation of the ComponentMarketParamsRef interface. Serves as a place holder for the market parameters needed to value the component object – discount curve, treasury curve, EDSF curve, credit curve, component quote, treasury quote map, and fixings map.
